In a coding language such words are written as – </br> "tree gives fruits" → "pin din nip" </br> "fruits make healthy" → "din sim kip" </br> "healthy fruits eat" → "din sim lin" </br> What is the code for "tree"? </br> किसी कोडिंग भाषा में शब्‍दों को इस प्रकार लिखा जाता है – </br> "tree" का कोड क्‍या होगा?@pin@sim@nip@Either (1) or (3)@4@